<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> A. Mingans: An ancient Syriac translation of the Kur'an in Bull. John Rylands Libr., ix <span class="c2">(١٩٢٥)</span>, ١٨٨ - ٢٣٥, and repr<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
